name: sap.watt.common.service.ui.WizardStep
description: The wizard step interface. Any wizard step that is intended to be available in the template creation wizards is a UI wizard part whose getContent method initiates the step UI (extending sap.watt.uitools.plugin.template.ui.wizard.WizardStepContent) with the this.context property, and returns the result of the getWizardStep method of the wizard service with the step content object, the step title, and description.
